Package: yfinanceDV
Title: Financial Data Visualization Package for Data Science Project 2023-2024
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
    given = "Weinan",
    family = "He",
    email = "weinan.he23@imperial.ac.uk",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package provides a comprehensive suite of tools for visualizing 
    financial data sourced from YAHOO. users can generate interactive plots, including 
    candlestick charts, simple moving averages, and volume bars. Additionally, the 
    package offers the flexibility to incorporate technical indicators such as Relative 
    strength index(RSI), Moving average convergence/divergence(MACD), and Stochastic 
    Oscillator, enabling deeper analysis of market trends and patterns.
